tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE evolutionary_changes (
    change_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    gene_id INT,
    factor_id INT,
    change_description TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (gene_id) REFERENCES gene_expression_data(gene_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (factor_id) REFERENCES environmental_factors(factor_id)
);

CREATE TABLE gene_evolution (
    evolution_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    gene_id INT,
    species_id INT,
    mutation_rate FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (gene_id) REFERENCES gene_expression_data(gene_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (species_id) REFERENCES species(species_id)
);

CREATE TABLE EvolutionaryChanges (
  change_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  gene_id UUID,
  factor_id UUID,
  change_type STRING,
  change_description STRING
);
